prompt_text: Describe your stay at a resort.
content_text: I had the privilege to stay in a resort last year when I visited Mountain Dew with my friends. It was expensive one definitely, but then again we love staying there. The room was neat and clean, the curtains were well and tidy and smooth. The restaurant also there is. It also offered fine dining and with wine. I enjoyed a lot with my friends. Had a good time, good coffee. And wonderful food. The people were also nice and the receptionist was very beautiful who helped us all through the state and I would like to visit it again. Thank you.
